text: Khojorni () is a small town (daba) in Georgia’s Kvemo Kartli region with the population of 635.. It had 842 inhabitants in 2002 https://www.citypopulation.de/en/georgia/kvemokartli/marneuli/44326031__khojorni/. ==References== Category:Populated places in Marneuli Municipality Category:Populated places in Kvemo Kartli
